data.description: Located in wonderful non-HOA subdivision in Powder Springs, GA, 10 mins to I-20.  Wonderful community home with 3 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms is located in a quiet subdivision located on a corner lot.  The home features a large master suite, bonus room downstairs with private bathroom, new water heater, screened in back deck with back patio, 2 car driveway with garage, and is conveniently located near plenty of shopping, restaurants, and great schools.
